          "text": [
            "Funciones de Synthetic Control definidas.\n",
            "  Covariables del DAG: bookings_mean, bookings_trend, weekend_ratio, sessions, gdp_per_capita, marketing_spend\n",
            "  V-weights: cross-validated (train 70% / val 30% del pre-periodo)\n",
            "  Diagnósticos: Positivity, Covariate Balance (SMD), V-sensitivity\n"
          ]
